data.description: Welcome to Tall Oaks Crossing and 1404 Peartree Lane. This center hall colonial is cited on a cul de sac with a spacious fenced rear yard and backing to tall trees. Wood floors, open kitchen, and main floor family room. Four bedrooms and two full bath's upstairs. Lower level recreation room, office and full bath. Laundry on two floors. Two car garage and plenty of storage space. Great yard and patio area. Community tennis, hike and bike trails, picnic areas and tot lots. Near to schools, shops, transportation and commuter routes. Come Live the Tall Oaks Crossing Lifestyle!
